OL,6,F"There's a story about when he wakes
OL,7,Fup the last morning of the pilgrimage
OL,8,Fand he is cured," he said.
OL,10,F"He leaps out of bed and he runs all
OL,11,Fthe way to the grotto from where he
OL,12,Fhas been staying.
OL,14,F"What I think was incredible being
OL,15,Fthere and seeing that distance and to
OL,16,Fthink about someone who hasn't walked
OL,17,Ffor years running bare foot at full
OL,18,Fspeed."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
