OL,3,CMan's recovery in 1923 declared first
OL,4,CEnglish miracle
OL,6,FDr Vallet had examined John Traynor in
OL,7,FJuly 1926, together with three
OL,8,FLiverpool doctors who had examined
OL,9,FJohn at Lourdes in 1923, both before
OL,10,Fand after his cure and had written a
OL,11,Freport.
OL,13,FThe report concluded: "We recognise
OL,14,Fand proclaim, along with our
OL,15,FConfreres, that the process of this
OL,16,Fprodigious healing is absolutely
OL,17,Foutside and above the forces of
OL,18,Fnature."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
