OL,3,CMan's recovery in 1923 declared first
OL,4,CEnglish miracle
OL,6,FDr Moriarty continued his research in
OL,7,Farchdiocesan archives and elsewhere,
OL,8,Fassembling an extensive dossier of
OL,9,Fevidence, and in particular
OL,10,Fcontemporaneous medical evidence,
OL,11,Frelating to the cure of John Traynor.
OL,12,FThis dossier was then sent to the
OL,13,Farchdiocese by Monseigneur Jean-Marc
OL,14,FMicas, the Bishop of Tarbes and
OL,15,FLourdes, over the summer.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
